      • parseMediaType

        public static MediaType parseMediaType(StringReader input)
                                throws IOException
        Parses a MediaType value, either from a HTTP header or from an application.
        参数:
        input - a reader over the header text
        返回:
        a MediaType parsed from the input, or null if not valid
        抛出:
        IOException - if there was a problem reading the input
